        <updateDate>2019-08-16T13:47:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Digital Taxonomy Act of 2019</b><br /><br />This bill requires the Federal Trade Commission to develop a plan for preventing unfair or deceptive practices relating to transactions involving digital tokens, including any recommendations for further action by Congress. Digital tokens include digital currency or cryptocurrency.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
